{"scenicName": "上海米哈游大厦", "city": "上海米哈游大厦", "scenes": [{"text": "大家好呀！我是红魔馆的门卫红美铃，今天带大家逛逛上海米哈游大厦！", "expression": "confident", "audioFile": "seg-00.mp3", "durationInFrames": 209, "imageFile": "vid_36f19f6e2fd8-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "这里可是中国游戏产业的耀眼地标，米哈游的大本营呢~", "expression": "happy_confident", "audioFile": "seg-01.mp3", "durationInFrames": 192, "imageFile": "vid_36f19f6e2fd8-img-01.jpg"}, {"text": "这座大厦坐落在上海徐汇区的漕河泾开发区，位置那叫一个繁华！", "expression": "happy3", "audioFile": "seg-02.mp3", "durationInFrames": 169, "imageFile": "vid_36f19f6e2fd8-img-02.jpg"}, {"text": "建筑面积约有五万平方米，现代感十足，像一艘科幻飞船！", "expression": "excited", "audioFile": "seg-03.mp3", "durationInFrames": 182, "imageFile": "vid_36f19f6e2fd8-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "米哈游在2011年由三个大学生创立，短短十年就成了全球大公司哦！", "expression": "thinking", "audioFile": "seg-04.mp3", "durationInFrames": 216, "imageFile": "vid_36f19f6e2fd8-img-01.jpg"}, {"text": "这座大厦是2019年投入使用的，见证了原神、崩坏系列的火爆呢。", "expression": "happy_confident", "audioFile": "seg-05.mp3", "durationInFrames": 204, "imageFile": "vid_36f19f6e2fd8-img-02.jpg"}, {"text": "据说选址时就看中了这里的创新氛围，果然选择太棒了！", "expression": "happy3", "audioFile": "seg-06.mp3", "durationInFrames": 235, "imageFile": "vid_36f19f6e2fd8-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "一进大厅你就会被震撼到——那座三米高的原神角色雕塑，帅气逼人！", "expression": "surprised", "audioFile": "seg-07.mp3", "durationInFrames": 212, "imageFile": "vid_36f19f6e2fd8-img-01.jpg"}, {"text": "走廊墙上全是崩坏系列的精美壁画，每一幅都在讲述热血故事。", "expression": "excited", "audioFile": "seg-08.mp3", "durationInFrames": 196, "imageFile": "vid_36f19f6e2fd8-img-02.jpg"}, {"text": "顶楼的观景台能俯瞰整个漕河泾，景色简直让人心旷神怡~", "expression": "happy5", "audioFile": "seg-09.mp3", "durationInFrames": 222, "imageFile": "vid_36f19f6e2fd8-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "还有专属的游戏体验区，能提前试玩未发布的新版本哦！", "expression": "excited", "audioFile": "seg-10.mp3", "durationInFrames": 179, "imageFile": "vid_36f19f6e2fd8-img-01.jpg"}, {"text": "员工咖啡厅里摆满了手办和周边，连拉花都是游戏角色的图案！", "expression": "surprised", "audioFile": "seg-11.mp3", "durationInFrames": 184, "imageFile": "vid_36f19f6e2fd8-img-02.jpg"}, {"text": "米哈游大厦不仅是个办公楼，更是二次元文化与科技融合的杰作！", "expression": "confident", "audioFile": "seg-12.mp3", "durationInFrames": 171, "imageFile": "vid_36f19f6e2fd8-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "它代表了中国原创游戏走向世界的标杆，激励着无数年轻人追梦。", "expression": "thinking", "audioFile": "seg-13.mp3", "durationInFrames": 166, "imageFile": "vid_36f19f6e2fd8-img-01.jpg"}, {"text": "这里的每一处设计都藏着彩蛋，连电梯按钮都是原神元素呢！", "expression": "confused", "audioFile": "seg-14.mp3", "durationInFrames": 175, "imageFile": "vid_36f19f6e2fd8-img-02.jpg"}, {"text": "对了，参观的话记得提前预约，工作日周一至周五才开放哦。", "expression": "happy5", "audioFile": "seg-15.mp3", "durationInFrames": 162, "imageFile": "vid_36f19f6e2fd8-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "建议上午十点来，人少光线好，拍照打卡最出片了~", "expression": "happy3", "audioFile": "seg-16.mp3", "durationInFrames": 178, "imageFile": "vid_36f19f6e2fd8-img-01.jpg"}, {"text": "注意部分区域禁止摄影，尤其是研发部门，要遵守规定呀。", "expression": "default", "audioFile": "seg-17.mp3", "durationInFrames": 196, "imageFile": "vid_36f19f6e2fd8-img-02.jpg"}, {"text": "米哈游大厦真的充满了创意和热情，来了就不想走呢！", "expression": "happy5", "audioFile": "seg-18.mp3", "durationInFrames": 178, "imageFile": "vid_36f19f6e2fd8-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "希望我的介绍能让大家爱上这里，红美铃随时等你再来探秘！", "expression": "confident", "audioFile": "seg-19.mp3", "durationInFrames": 167, "imageFile": "vid_36f19f6e2fd8-img-01.jpg"}, {"text": "那么旅途愉快，咱们下次再见咯！", "expression": "happy5", "audioFile": "seg-20.mp3", "durationInFrames": 168, "imageFile": "vid_36f19f6e2fd8-img-02.jpg"}], "totalFrames": 4051}